  "operation_name": "aclnnAdaLayerNormV2",
  "description": "接口功能：AdaLayerNormV2算子将LayerNorm和下游的Add、Mul融合起来，通过自适应参数scale和shift来调整归一化过程。相比AdaLayerNorm算子，输出新增2个参数（输入的均值和输入的标准差的倒数）；weight和bias支持的数据类型增加对应约束。\n\n计算公式：\n$$\nout = LayerNorm(x) * (1 + scale) + shift\n$$\n\nLayerNorm计算公式：\n$$\nmean = E(x)\n$$\n\n$$\nrstd = {1.0\\over\\sqrt {Var(x)+epsilon}}\n$$\n\n$$\nLayerNorm(x) = (x-mean) * rstd * weightOptional + biasOptional\n$$\n\n其中，E(x)表示输入的均值，Var(x)表示输入的方差。",
  "api_flow": "two-step",
  "inter_parameter_constraints": [
    {
      "type": "shape_choice",
      "params": [
        "x",
        "scale"
      ],
      "expr": "(len(scale.shape) == len(x.shape) - 1 and scale.shape[:-1] == x.shape[:-2] and scale.shape[-1] == x.shape[-1]) or (len(scale.shape) == len(x.shape) and scale.shape[:-2] == x.shape[:-2] and scale.shape[-2] == 1 and scale.shape[-1] == x.shape[-1])",
      "description": "scale的shape必须为[B, H]或[B, 1, H]，其中前导B维度数量和大小与x的前导B维一致，最后一维与x的H维一致。",
      "source": "x",
      "target": [
        "scale"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "shape_choice",
      "params": [
        "x",
        "shift"
      ],
      "expr": "(len(shift.shape) == len(x.shape) - 1 and shift.shape[:-1] == x.shape[:-2] and shift.shape[-1] == x.shape[-1]) or (len(shift.shape) == len(x.shape) and shift.shape[:-2] == x.shape[:-2] and shift.shape[-2] == 1 and shift.shape[-1] == x.shape[-1])",
      "description": "shift的shape必须为[B, H]或[B, 1, H]，其中前导B维度数量和大小与x的前导B维一致，最后一维与x的H维一致。",
      "source": "x",
      "target": [
        "shift"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "shape_dependency",
      "params": [
        "x",
        "weightOptional"
      ],
      "expr": "weightOptional is None or (len(weightOptional.shape) == 1 and weightOptional.shape[0] == x.shape[-1])",
      "description": "weightOptional存在时，其shape必须为[H]，且H与x的最后一维一致。",
